messages.messageBody:
Hi folks,

I've been reading stuff on Ralph Nader. It's quite different than Gore
or Bush or Bore or Gush. He's predicted to get 15% of the vote in
Alaska. He's bringing out some important issues. Nader is from the
Green Party. I have no idea of his stand on homeschooling. His running
mate is a Native American gal from a Minnesota Indian Reservation. The
problem with a third party in this election is that mostly only
Republicans and Democrats have a chance. Next Tues. at our
homeschooling meeting we will be discussing the upcoming election.

Sherry
From Upper Michigan,USA
